      "title": "President and Opposition Leader hold talks",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A discussion between President Ranil Wickremesinghe and Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa was reportedly held at the Presidential Secretariat in Colombo on Monday.",
        "The general secretary of the \u2018Samagi Jana Balawegaya\u2019, MP Ranjith Madduma Bandara had also participated in the meeting, according to sources.",
        "It is reported that the discussion focused on the formation of the proposed all-party government."
      ],
